# What Cloud Build uploads as the build context.
#
# Without this file gcloud derives the ignore list from .gitignore, which
# excludes artifacts/ -- and both Dockerfiles COPY artifacts/. The build would
# fail on a missing directory that exists perfectly well on disk.
#
# So: artifacts/ and data/sample/ are deliberately INCLUDED here, and .env is
# deliberately excluded. Never upload credentials to a build context.

.git/
.github/
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
tests/
notebooks/

# Credentials — never.
.env
*.json.key
service-account*.json

# Local-only
*.md
!README.md
